---
---

<section class="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="about__grid">
    <div class="about__img-wrap" data-animate="image">
      <img
        src="/images/about.jpg"
        alt="Sanchi Enterprises exhibition carpet installation"
        class="about__img"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        width="800"
        height="600"
        style="object-position: center 25%"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="about__body" data-animate data-delay="1">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--line">About Sanchi Enterprises</span>
      <h2 class="section-title about__title" id="about-heading">
        In the Industry<br />Since 1995.
      </h2>
      <p class="about__text">
        For over 30 years, Sanchi Enterprises has been supplying exhibition
        carpets and flooring solutions to India's trade fairs, expos, and
        conventions. We work directly with exhibition organizers, event
        agencies, and expo contractors — understanding the deadlines,
        the logistics, and the precision the industry demands.
      </p>
      <p class="about__text">
        From material supply and on-site installation to edge finishing
        and live-day maintenance — we manage the complete flooring
        operation for India's trade fairs and exhibitions.
      </p>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn--ghost-dark">
        About Sanchi
        <svg width="12" height="10" viewBox="0 0 12 10" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M1 5h10M7 1l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"
            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
